  "description": "在E3展会上，微软还宣布，其还将发布一个<a href=\"http://www.neowin.net/news/microsoft-announces-redesigned-xbox-360-console-available-today\" target=\"_blank\">升级版的Xbox 360</a>。<b>国外知名拆解团队iFixit在第一时间就拿到了新版Xbox 360机器，在打开之后发现，新机器看起来很容易修复，iFixit因此给予了8分的评级(满分10分)。</b>新版Xbox 360的内部高度模块化，这使得其很容易更换部件。此外，驱动器的更换也很方便，不过它需要有专用的Xbox驱动器才能用(这一点与此前相同)。<br /><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d431491/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241032.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E8%A7%A3%E5%89%96%E6%96%B0%E7%89%88Xbox+360%EF%BC%9A%E7%BB%B4%E4%BF%AE%E6%9B%B4%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241032.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E8%A7%A3%E5%89%96%E6%96%B0%E7%89%88Xbox+360%EF%BC%9A%E7%BB%B4%E4%BF%AE%E6%9B%B4%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241032.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E8%A7%A3%E5%89%96%E6%96%B0%E7%89%88Xbox+360%EF%BC%9A%E7%BB%B4%E4%BF%AE%E6%9B%B4%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241032.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E8%A7%A3%E5%89%96%E6%96%B0%E7%89%88Xbox+360%EF%BC%9A%E7%BB%B4%E4%BF%AE%E6%9B%B4%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241032.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E8%